name: Cute Girl Dash Blocks Edition
description:
Cute Girl Dash - Blocks Edition!

Try to stay on the blocks but can you react fast enough? Your path is being built in real time with exciting combinations. Listen to the awesome background music remix as you advance through the levels in this fun game!

How to play:

• Fun music
• Tap to jump
• Don't fall off
• Collect the jewels
• Unlock all of the characters - New ones to come!

How far can you go?
